  ?paper dblp:publishedIn "SIGIR" .
  OPTIONAL { ?paper dblp:title ?title }
  OPTIONAL { ?paper dblp:yearOfPublication ?year }
}
```

This matches the actual data in the knowledge graph and will retrieve all papers published in SIGIR, with their titles and publication years.

